data.description: Welcome to your charming 3-bed, 2-bath brick ranch in West Ashley, Charleston. Built in 1958, this home combines vintage appeal with modern updates. The renovated kitchen and baths, along with updated flooring, add a touch of contemporary luxury. With a bonus room, it's perfect for versatile use.Convenience is at your doorstep with proximity to shopping, dining, downtown Charleston, and the beach. The spacious backyard, complete with utility sheds and a full covered patio beckons relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. No HOA adds flexibility, and being in an X Flood Zone provides peace of mind. Don't miss out on this delightful home in a prime location!This listing qualifies for up to a 1% reduced interest rate through preferred lender. Contact Becky Kendall for more infoat becky.kendall@getevolved.com.
